<section class="reviews-section" id="customer-reviews">
  <div class="reviews-inner">

    <div class="reviews-head reveal">
      <span class="reviews-eyebrow">Verified Reviews</span>
      <h2 class="reviews-title">What people are <em>saying</em></h2>
      <div class="reviews-summary">
        <div class="reviews-stars" aria-label="4.8 out of 5 stars">
          <span>★</span><span>★</span><span>★</span><span>★</span><span>★</span>
        </div>
        <div class="reviews-summary-text">
          <strong>4.8</strong> out of 5 · Verified purchases
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="reviews-grid">

      <article class="review-card reveal">
        <div class="review-stars">★★★★★</div>
        <h3 class="review-title">"Didn't expect to feel this calm at 7am"</h3>
        <p class="review-body">I bought this mostly for the gua sha but the full routine genuinely became my favorite 5 minutes of the day. Jawline looks tighter after 3 weeks, and the ice roller in the morning is unreal for de-puffing after bad sleep. Packaging felt way more premium than the price. The only "downside" is I now guilt-trip myself if I skip a day.</p>
        <footer class="review-meta">
          <div class="review-author">
            <span class="review-name">Sofia M.</span>
            <span class="review-verified" aria-label="Verified purchase">✓ Verified</span>
          </div>
          <div class="review-product">Complete Ritual</div>
        </footer>
      </article>

      <article class="review-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="review-stars">★★★★★</div>
        <h3 class="review-title">"The ice roller alone is worth it"</h3>
        <p class="review-body">I've tried the viral ones from Amazon and they always leaked or smelled like plastic. This one actually holds the cold, feels solid in your hand, and doesn't drip. I use it every morning after coffee and my under-eyes look like I slept 8 hours (I did not). Instant fix on hangover mornings too, not that I'd know.</p>
        <footer class="review-meta">
          <div class="review-author">
            <span class="review-name">Jess R.</span>
            <span class="review-verified" aria-label="Verified purchase">✓ Verified</span>
          </div>
          <div class="review-product">Ice Roller</div>
        </footer>
      </article>

      <article class="review-card reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <div class="review-stars">★★★★<span class="star-dim">★</span></div>
        <h3 class="review-title">"Skeptical husband, now he steals mine"</h3>
        <p class="review-body">Bought this thinking it was another skincare gimmick. Two weeks in, my cheekbones look more defined and my jaw tension from grinding at night is noticeably better. I follow the little guide they include and do it with the rosehip oil. 4 stars only because I wish it came in a pouch — I'm paranoid about dropping the stone. Otherwise perfect.</p>
        <footer class="review-meta">
          <div class="review-author">
            <span class="review-name">Amelia T.</span>
            <span class="review-verified" aria-label="Verified purchase">✓ Verified</span>
          </div>
          <div class="review-product">Amethyst Gua Sha</div>
        </footer>
      </article>

      <article class="review-card reveal reveal-delay-3">
        <div class="review-stars">★★★★★</div>
        <h3 class="review-title">"Rosehip oil that actually absorbs"</h3>
        <p class="review-body">I have combination skin and oils usually terrify me. This one sinks in within a minute and doesn't leave that greasy film. My dark spots from old acne are fading faster than with the $45 one I was using before. Bottle is small but a few drops is all you need — I'm 6 weeks in and barely made a dent.</p>
        <footer class="review-meta">
          <div class="review-author">
            <span class="review-name">Priya K.</span>
            <span class="review-verified" aria-label="Verified purchase">✓ Verified</span>
          </div>
          <div class="review-product">Rosehip Oil</div>
        </footer>
      </article>

      <article class="review-card reveal reveal-delay-4">
        <div class="review-stars">★★★★★</div>
        <h3 class="review-title">"Bought for my mum, stole it back"</h3>
        <p class="review-body">Ordered this as a birthday gift and ended up buying a second one for myself the next week. The roller is so relaxing after screen time that I've replaced my evening phone scroll with it. My skin looks less tired, I fall asleep faster, and honestly it just feels like a little ritual of self-respect. Exactly what the name promises.</p>
        <footer class="review-meta">
          <div class="review-author">
            <span class="review-name">Laura D.</span>
            <span class="review-verified" aria-label="Verified purchase">✓ Verified</span>
          </div>
          <div class="review-product">Complete Ritual</div>
        </footer>
      </article>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
/* ── Customer Reviews Section ── */
.reviews-section {
  background: var(--cream);
  padding: var(--space-section-y) var(--space-section-x);
}

.reviews-inner {
  max-width: var(--page-default);
  margin: 0 auto;
}

/* Header */
.reviews-head {
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: clamp(48px, 6vw, 80px);
}

.reviews-eyebrow {
  display: inline-block;
  font-family: var(--sans);
  font-size: 10px;
  letter-spacing: 0.35em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--terracotta);
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.reviews-title {
  font-family: var(--serif);
  font-size: clamp(36px, 5vw, 64px);
  font-weight: 300;
  color: var(--espresso);
  line-height: 1.05;
  letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  margin-bottom: 28px;
}

.reviews-title em {
  font-style: italic;
  color: var(--terracotta);
}

.reviews-summary {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 16px;
  padding: 14px 24px;
  background: var(--white);
  border: 1px solid var(--cream-dark);
  border-radius: 999px;
}

.reviews-stars {
  display: inline-flex;
  gap: 2px;
  color: var(--terracotta);
  font-size: 18px;
  letter-spacing: 1px;
}

.reviews-summary-text {
  font-family: var(--sans);
  font-size: 13px;
  color: var(--stone);
}

.reviews-summary-text strong {
  font-family: var(--serif);
  font-size: 22px;
  font-weight: 400;
  color: var(--espresso);
  margin-right: 4px;
}

/* Grid */
.reviews-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 24px;
}

/* Review card */
.review-card {
  background: var(--white);
  border: 1px solid var(--cream-dark);
  padding: 36px 32px;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  transition: transform 0.5s var(--ease-premium), box-shadow 0.5s var(--ease-premium);
}

.review-card:hover {
  transform: translateY(-4px);
  box-shadow: 0 20px 40px -20px rgba(30, 18, 10, 0.12);
}

.review-stars {
  font-size: 16px;
  color: var(--terracotta);
  letter-spacing: 3px;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.review-stars .star-dim {
  color: var(--cream-dark);
}

.review-title {
  font-family: var(--serif);
  font-size: 22px;
  font-weight: 400;
  color: var(--espresso);
  line-height: 1.25;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
  font-style: italic;
}

.review-body {
  font-family: var(--sans);
  font-size: 14px;
  line-height: 1.75;
  color: var(--stone);
  margin-bottom: 28px;
  flex-grow: 1;
}

.review-meta {
  padding-top: 20px;
  border-top: 1px solid var(--cream-dark);
}

.review-author {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between;
  margin-bottom: 6px;
}

.review-name {
  font-family: var(--serif);
  font-size: 16px;
  font-weight: 500;
  color: var(--espresso);
}

.review-verified {
  font-family: var(--sans);
  font-size: 10px;
  letter-spacing: 0.15em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--terracotta);
  font-weight: 500;
}

.review-product {
  font-family: var(--sans);
  font-size: 11px;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  color: var(--stone);
  opacity: 0.75;
  text-transform: uppercase;
}

/* ── Responsive ── */
@media (max-width: 1024px) {
  .reviews-grid {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 20px;
  }
  .review-card {
    padding: 32px 28px;
  }
}

@media (max-width: 640px) {
  .reviews-grid {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 16px;
  }
  .review-card {
    padding: 28px 24px;
  }
  .review-title {
    font-size: 20px;
  }
  .review-summary {
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
  }
}
</style>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Customer Reviews",
  "presets": [{ "name": "Customer Reviews" }]
}
{% endschema %}
